sources.title: Queen Kong - Full Movie
sources.description:
Click here to watch great FREE Movies & TV: http://filmrise.com

In this campy, action-packed parody of the original “King Kong”, an all-female film crew journeys to Africa where a giant ape, Queen Kong, falls in love with the crew's male star – Ray Fay (B-movie stalwart  Robin Askwith). Having been banned from screens for over 25 years due to a slew of legal disputes, the film is now available to see in all of it’s bizarre glory!
